1
00:01:29,720 --> 00:01:30,680
Miss Chuyun.

2
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,160
Don't be afraid.

3
00:01:32,160 --> 00:01:33,360
You are safe now.

4
00:01:34,800 --> 00:01:37,039
Benefactor, is that you?

5
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,560
I thought something happened to you.

6
00:01:38,560 --> 00:01:40,039
I looked for you for so long.

7
00:01:40,039 --> 00:01:40,520
I...

8
00:01:43,880 --> 00:01:46,039
Do you know where those two came from?

9
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:48,120
Where can I sleep?

10
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,560
You bumped my head.

11
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,000
Honestly,

12
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:02,530
coming to a girl's room in the middle of the night is so improper.

13
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,760
Your room is less than a hundred meters from mine.

14
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,680
You won't die.

15
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:18,560
If I really can't go more than 100 steps from her,

16
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,000
how do I get out?

17
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:55,960
Where is she going so late at night?

18
00:02:57,760 --> 00:02:58,560
Staying over.

19
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,640
No one is staying over.

20
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:04,960
The two people who came to the cabin the other day.

21
00:03:05,880 --> 00:03:07,720
Don't you know them?

22
00:03:08,040 --> 00:03:09,720
Oh, you mean them.

23
00:03:10,080 --> 00:03:11,120
I don't know them.

24
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:12,480
I...

25
00:03:12,680 --> 00:03:14,480
They suddenly appeared in the cabin.

26
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:17,720
I was scared to death, and then I forgot.

27
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:22,040
These two look a bit suspicious.

28
00:03:22,640 --> 00:03:23,840
If you get the chance,

29
00:03:23,840 --> 00:03:24,520
could you help me

30
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,000
look into them?

31
00:03:26,680 --> 00:03:27,680
Of course.

32
00:03:28,240 --> 00:03:29,760
Since it is your request,

33
00:03:30,040 --> 00:03:33,040
I'd risk my life without hesitation.

34
00:03:36,760 --> 00:03:39,880
There's no need for such sacrifice.

35
00:03:40,040 --> 00:03:42,240
Just keep an eye on them for me.

36
00:03:45,680 --> 00:03:46,560
Benefactor.

37
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:48,840
Where have you been these days?

38
00:03:49,079 --> 00:03:50,880
Why didn't you come to the cabin?

39
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,280
I thought...

40
00:03:52,280 --> 00:03:55,079
...you had been harmed by someone.

41
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,800
I was really scared.

42
00:04:00,200 --> 00:04:00,720
Don't be scared.

43
00:04:00,720 --> 00:04:01,680
I'm fine.

44
00:04:02,040 --> 00:04:04,720
I just had some matters to attend to,

45
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,130
so I was away for a while.

46
00:04:09,160 --> 00:04:10,620
I'm just glad you're okay.

47
00:04:13,680 --> 00:04:16,000
Benefactor, where are we now?

48
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:18,000
This isn't the bed in the wooden hut.

49
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,740
We are at the medical hall.

50
00:04:20,760 --> 00:04:23,880
Why did you bring me to Sitai Town?

51
00:04:24,040 --> 00:04:26,770
It's been some time since your family was harmed.

52
00:04:27,080 --> 00:04:29,840
The killers must assume

53
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,740
you died in the mountains.

54
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:34,280
You are very safe here.

55
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,920
It is convenient at the medical hall,

56
00:04:35,920 --> 00:04:37,520
where I can treat your eyes.

57
00:04:39,000 --> 00:04:40,080
But...

58
00:04:40,480 --> 00:04:42,760
my father offended Master Du.

59
00:04:43,720 --> 00:04:45,800
How could he tolerate me?

60
00:04:46,680 --> 00:04:48,010
Don't worry about that.

61
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:51,360
My father originally wanted us to marry.

62
00:04:51,480 --> 00:04:53,560
That is how the feud with your father began.

63
00:04:53,560 --> 00:04:56,040
But it's not a blood feud.

64
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,480
Given time,

65
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,560
I'm sure I can persuade him.

66
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,640
My father humiliated you,

67
00:05:04,040 --> 00:05:05,640
yet you still saved me.

68
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:10,160
I really don't know how to repay you.

69
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,720
As they say, healers have kind hearts.

70
00:05:15,120 --> 00:05:17,160
My family has practiced medicine for generations.

71
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:19,480
I had to help.

72
00:05:21,520 --> 00:05:22,920
When my eyes heal,

73
00:05:23,440 --> 00:05:24,720
if you don't mind,

74
00:05:24,960 --> 00:05:26,520
I'll stay and serve you

75
00:05:26,800 --> 00:05:28,130
to repay your kindness.

76
00:05:29,000 --> 00:05:31,680
I have nowhere else to go anyway.

77
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:33,920
Alright.

78
00:05:34,440 --> 00:05:37,240
The most important thing now is for you to recover.

79
00:05:37,360 --> 00:05:39,800
We can talk about the rest later.

80
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:53,060
It is indeed troublesome.

81
00:05:53,760 --> 00:05:56,220
It seems Ji Bai and the others showing up here

82
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,760
was just an accident.

83
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:30,280
Don't worry, we travel fast.

84
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:32,240
Gushan isn't far from here.

85
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:34,500
We can deliver it in four or five days.

86
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:38,520
Why is your stall so deserted?

87
00:06:39,360 --> 00:06:41,360
I don't see any packages or letters.

88
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,800
I can tell you just returned from out of town.

89
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,760
In our town,

90
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:48,880
the Yan Family Escort Agency opened in the last two years.

91
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,159
They can deliver anything,

92
00:06:50,159 --> 00:06:51,620
with no limit on distance.

93
00:06:51,760 --> 00:06:53,600
They can go as far as the Capital.

94
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:57,180
For small businesses like us that only deliver nearby,

95
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:59,060
business has naturally dried up.

96
00:06:59,280 --> 00:07:01,680
And this Escort Agency has a good location,

97
00:07:01,680 --> 00:07:05,360
right in the northwest corner of the town center.

98
00:07:06,680 --> 00:07:08,480
Northwest corner of the market.

99
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:14,600
I heard they came here looking for someone at first.

100
00:07:14,960 --> 00:07:16,280
Since they couldn't find them,

101
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:18,640
they just set up camp here.

102
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,640
I don't know exactly where they're from,

103
00:07:21,640 --> 00:07:23,500
but you shouldn't mess with them.

104
00:07:24,040 --> 00:07:26,120
They have powerful martial arts skills

105
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:27,320
and great influence.

106
00:07:27,640 --> 00:07:29,320
They are not to be trifled with.

107
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:31,320
Okay. Thank you for your help, Boss.

108
00:07:31,400 --> 00:07:32,159
Thank you.

109
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:36,159
Be careful. This place isn't safe.

110
00:07:45,840 --> 00:07:47,159
It's her.

111
00:08:04,640 --> 00:08:07,520
These alleys look almost exactly the same.

112
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:09,370
Something's wrong.

113
00:08:11,840 --> 00:08:14,040
Catch her! Don't let her get away!

114
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:31,160
Stop!

115
00:08:31,960 --> 00:08:33,760
Don't let him get away. Hurry up!

116
00:08:38,520 --> 00:08:39,440
Stop!

117
00:08:45,280 --> 00:08:46,320
There she is!

118
00:08:47,200 --> 00:08:48,460
Don't let her get away!

119
00:08:49,760 --> 00:08:50,800
Over there!

120
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:54,560
Just a rat in a trap.

121
00:09:04,760 --> 00:09:06,280
That kid must have jumped the wall.

122
00:09:06,280 --> 00:09:07,360
Split up!

123
00:09:07,360 --> 00:09:08,040
Yes, sir!

124
00:09:15,040 --> 00:09:17,120
They know the terrain too well.

125
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,580
They couldn't have gone far. Search.

126
00:09:40,600 --> 00:09:42,120
Yes, sir. Let's go.

127
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,560
Public morals are declining day by day.

128
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,560
Truly.

129
00:10:05,760 --> 00:10:07,760
Let's go. Check over there.

130
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:48,020
This is the third time I've saved you.

131
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:51,320
Thanks.

132
00:10:51,400 --> 00:10:52,840
Just a verbal thank you?

133
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:54,560
If I hadn't happened to see you leave

134
00:10:54,560 --> 00:10:55,720
and followed you,

135
00:10:55,840 --> 00:10:58,100
wouldn't you be dead in the clinic by now?

136
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:02,570
You're still laughing.

137
00:11:06,000 --> 00:11:06,960
I know now.

138
00:11:07,840 --> 00:11:08,960
You tricked me.

139
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:12,280
There's no such thing as a poison that kills in a hundred steps.

140
00:11:12,280 --> 00:11:13,940
I can't believe I trusted you.

141
00:11:19,800 --> 00:11:21,040
It seems

142
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:24,160
you're actually stupid, not just pretending.

143
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,460
You're the stupid one.

144
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,280
I just haven't traveled enough.

145
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:33,160
Everything I know comes from books.

146
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:36,840
Otherwise, how could I have been fooled by you?

147
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,600
Are you hurt badly?

148
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,460
It's nothing serious.

149
00:11:52,480 --> 00:11:55,360
Why are you out here in the middle of the night?

150
00:11:56,760 --> 00:11:59,320
I intended to write to my master

151
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:02,320
to ask her to come study Miss Chuyun's poison.

152
00:12:02,800 --> 00:12:04,960
But I ran into those people on the way.

153
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:06,840
Luckily, you were following me.

154
00:12:06,840 --> 00:12:08,900
Otherwise, I would be in big trouble.

155
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,600
I followed you all the way.

156
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:11,640
When I reached the alley entrance,

157
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,360
I saw you wandering around inside,

158
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,840
but then you suddenly disappeared.

159
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,760
I kept walking and ended up here.

160
00:12:22,400 --> 00:12:24,330
Who were those people chasing you?

161
00:12:27,120 --> 00:12:28,360
I'm not sure,

162
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:30,440
but their leader...

163
00:12:30,840 --> 00:12:33,240
I think I saw him at Prince Zhenbei's Manor.

164
00:12:35,760 --> 00:12:37,720
They really tracked us here.

165
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,560
What's wrong?

166
00:12:48,920 --> 00:12:51,120
Let's go back to the medical hall first.

167
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,120
But I have somewhere else to go.

168
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,520
I'll go with you.

169
00:13:07,760 --> 00:13:08,560
Get on.

170
00:13:09,080 --> 00:13:10,520
It's not your first time.

171
00:13:10,640 --> 00:13:11,500
Why are you shy?

172
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:33,720
Everyone here is a skilled fighter.

173
00:13:33,880 --> 00:13:36,880
Strangers might mistake this place for a military camp.

174
00:13:36,880 --> 00:13:38,680
It really is connected to him.

175
00:13:43,360 --> 00:13:44,420
Connected to whom?

176
00:13:46,760 --> 00:13:47,880
An old friend.

177
00:13:48,880 --> 00:13:51,560
He lived here for a while,

178
00:13:51,560 --> 00:13:54,320
but later moved to the mountains for some reason,

179
00:13:54,320 --> 00:13:56,240
leaving this place empty.

180
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,400
From the looks of it,

181
00:13:59,640 --> 00:14:02,160
he probably isn't here anymore.

182
00:14:04,520 --> 00:14:06,320
Is that old friend you mentioned

183
00:14:07,360 --> 00:14:08,640
named Jiujiu?

184
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:12,000
Do you know him?

185
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:49,960
Wu, Zhang, Li, Zheng, Chen, Luo, Deng,

186
00:14:48,160 --> 00:14:49,440
Yi, Yi, Nan,

187
00:14:49,440 --> 00:14:51,040
Xiao, Xiao, Xue, Yi, Yi, Nan.

188
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,480
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

189
00:15:18,520 --> 00:15:19,520
Ma, Miao, Lu, Ran.

190
00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:23,960
Fen,

191
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,440
Pan, Xiu, Long,

192
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:24,240
Lu, Sun, Zhang, Meng,

193
00:15:24,440 --> 00:15:24,600
Yi.
